<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link type="text/css" href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link type="text/css" href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-static-top" style="border-bottom:3px solid #64ace0; box-shadow: 0px 1px 2px #333">
        <div class="navbar-inner">
            <ul class="nav pull-right">
                <li><a href="${metadata['repo_url']}"><i class="icon-gift icon-white"></i> Source Repository</a></li>
                <li><a href="${metadata['dev_thread_url']}"><i class="icon-comment icon-white"></i> Discuss at TT-Forums.net</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br />
    <div class="container">
        <img src="img/masthead.png" class="pull-right" style="padding-top:12px;"/>
        <h1>Squid Ate FISH</h1>
        <hr />
        <h3>${len(vehicles)} ships for OpenTTD</h3>
        <ul class="inline">
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Intro dates ${metadata['dates'][0]}-${metadata['dates'][1]}</li>
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Wide range of ship types and capacities</li>
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Compatible with all known cargos</li>
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Supports 2 company colours</li>
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Autorefit support</li>
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Parameter for ship speed</li>
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Parameter for canal construction costs</li>
            <li><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> GPL v2 license</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="alert alert-info">Just one little problem: it's not finished yet ;)</p>
        <hr />
        <table class="table table-striped">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ship Name</th>
                    <th class="number">Intro Date</th>
                    <th>Extra Info</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tal:build_vehicles_list repeat="vehicle vehicles">
                    <tr>
                        <td>${vehicle.get_name_substr()} ${base_lang_strings[vehicle.get_str_name_suffix()]}</td>
                        <td class="number">${vehicle.intro_date}</td>
                        <td>${base_lang_strings[vehicle.get_str_type_info()]}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tal:build_vehicles_list>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center; color:#999; padding:5px; background-color:#eee; border-top:solid 1px #ddd; box-shadow: inset 0px 1px 1px #ddd">Fish Ate Squid, with thanks to all who helped</div>
</body>

</html>
